    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox to a mechanical M Variable Differential Lock. The vehicle has undergone proactive maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and valve shim adjustment to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis remains taut with no subframe fatigue detected during recent inspection. While the exterior shows honest road wear, the suspension kinematics and steering rack feedback remain sharp, offering the precise, analog engagement sought by purists. This is a mechanically sound example optimized for performance driving.",
