    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-cared-for 2018 BMW X5 xDrive35i finished in timeless Black Sapphire Metallic. This vehicle has served as a reliable daily driver and presents beautifully, showing only the honest character of a car that has been carefully enjoyed. The exterior paint retains a deep, high gloss; upon close inspection, you will find minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch near the rear passenger wheel well\u2014standard for its age and hardly noticeable from a few feet away. Inside, the Mocha Dakota leather interior is smoke-free and plush. The driver\u2019s side seat bolster shows very light entry wear, but the remaining seats and the cabin materials remain in excellent shape. All premium features, including the panoramic sunroof, navigation system, and multi-zone climate control, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is robust with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive turbocharged engine. It has been serviced regularly, with a fresh oil change and brake fluid flush performed just last month. The tires have approximately 60% tread remaining, and the car drives straight and true. This is a solid, dependable luxury SUV that offers premium comfort without the new-car price tag. Clean title in hand.",
